list.abstract: seed（英 [siːd]，美 [siːd]），英语单词，作名词为种子；籽；种子选手。作动词为在…上播种；结籽；脱籽。短语搭配有seed money（种子基金）。例句为“After that, the seed can start growing.（之后，种子可以开始生长。）” seed相关近义词有foundation、child等。
seed，是《机动战士高达SEED》系列作品术语。SEED，全称“Superior Evolutionary Element Destined-factor”, 直译为有高级进化要素的命运基因。

yingyinNormal.en: Grandpa! Grandpa! I want to plant a seed!
yingyinNormal.zh: 爷爷！我想种一颗种子！

yingyinNormal.en: We got to get the Seed before Galvatron does.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们必须比惊破天早一步抢到种子。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa and George are waiting for the seed to grow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩佩和乔治在等这颗种子长大。

yingyinNormal.en: This seed will grow into a lovely strawberry plant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这颗种子会长成一株漂亮的草莓。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait. The Seed? Those nasty soldiers that were chasing us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么种子？那些追杀我们的军人。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like to plant a strawberry seed? Yes, please!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想种一颗草莓种子吗？是的，愿意！

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa has lots of flower seeds. George only has one flower seed, but it is quite a big seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇有很多种子，而乔治只有一个种子，可是它的种子非常的大。

yingyinNormal.en: Peppa has lots of flower seeds. George only has one flower seed, but it is quite a big seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 佩奇有很多种子，而乔治只有一个种子，可是它的种子非常的大。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like to plant a strawberry seed? Yes, please. This seed will grow into a lovely strawberry plant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想不想种一粒草莓种子？是的，我想！到时候这里种子会长出一颗可爱的草莓苗。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like to plant a strawberry seed? Yes, please! This seed will grow into a lovely strawberry plant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想不想种一粒草莓种子？是的，我想！到时候这里种子会长出一颗可爱的草莓苗。

yingyinNormal.en: Seeds? What do seeds do? Seeds grow into plants. I just make a little hole and put the seed in. Then I cover it with earth and water it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 种子？种子是干什么的？种子会长出植物来。我只要挖一个小坑，把种子放进去。然后用土盖住，最后浇水。

yingyinNormal.en: Seeds? What do seeds do? Seeds grow into plants. I just make a little hole and put the seed in. Then I cover it with earth and water it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 种子？种子是干什么的？种子会长出植物来。我只要挖一个小坑，把种子放进去。然后用土盖住，最后浇水。

yingyinNormal.en: So what about the deal? Is it done? Did you get the Seed?
yingyinNormal.zh: 事情办好没？拿到种子了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. I want you to bring me the Seed, but I want you to bring it to me there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把种子带到中国给我。

yingyinNormal.en: I saw them board the ship, and they took something that they called the Seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看见他们上船，把一个叫种子的东西带走。

yingyinNormal.en: Just look at this seed. It's small. It's brown. It weighs hardly anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看看这粒种子，身躯渺小，色泽黯淡。轻若无物。

yingyinNormal.en: But, Attinger, buddy, for both our sakes, you need to deliver the Seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是艾汀杰为了我们两个好，你必须给我说好的种子。

yingyinNormal.en: And inside this apple are more seeds. To make more apple trees! Exactly! Grandpa! Grandpa! I want to plant a seed!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们看苹果里面还有很多这样的种子。可以长出更多的苹果！说得没错！爷爷！爷爷！我想种下一粒种子！

yingyinNormal.en: First, make a little hole. Then I put the seed in and cover it with earth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首先，挖一个小洞。然后我把这颗种子放进去，盖上土。

yingyinNormal.en: And sequoias are the largest single life form on Earth. All from a tiny seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 巨杉是地球孕育出的最大单体生命，就来自这一粒渺小的种子。
